==> 547 <==
From maechler@stat.math.ethz.ch  Fri May 19 21:11:52 2000
Received: from stat.math.ethz.ch (daemon@hypatia.ethz.ch [129.132.58.23])
	by pubhealth.ku.dk (8.9.3/8.9.1) with ESMTP id VAA02032
